<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.3">
<l>aṭicēr muṭiyiṉa rāki yaracarka ṭāntoḻa</l>
<l>iṭicēr muracaṅkaṇ muṟṟat tiyampa viruntavar</l>
<l>poṭicēr tukaḷāyp pōvar kaḷātali ṉokkeṉa</l>
<l>kaṭicēr tuḻāymuṭik kaṇṇaṉ kaḻalka ṇiṉaimiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Because those who sat, while kings worshipped [them], [their] heads</l>
<l>joined to [their] feet, while in the front yard thundering drums sounded,</l>
<l>will go as dust joined to ashes, instantly</l>
<l>think you of the ankletted [feet] of Kṛṣṇa with a pefumed tulsi crown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
